00:09:22.070 --> 00:09:24.506
This will be my testimony
and my summation.

00:09:24.506 --> 00:09:26.157
- Take the oath.

00:09:26.157 --> 00:09:28.240
- Do you swear to tell the
truth, the whole truth,

00:09:28.240 --> 00:09:29.700
and nothing but the
truth, so help you God?

00:09:29.700 --> 00:09:30.200
- I do.

00:09:34.405 --> 00:09:36.030
- Thousands of years
ago, the first man

00:09:36.030 --> 00:09:38.240
discovered how to make fire.

00:09:38.240 --> 00:09:39.920
He was probably
burned at the stake

00:09:39.920 --> 00:09:42.210
he taught his brothers to
light, but he left them

00:09:42.210 --> 00:09:44.190
a gift they had not conceived.

00:09:44.190 --> 00:09:46.710
And he lit the
darkness off the Earth.

00:09:46.710 --> 00:09:48.420
Throughout the
centuries, there were

00:09:48.420 --> 00:09:52.170
men who took first steps down
new roads armed with nothing

00:09:52.170 --> 00:09:54.060
but their own vision.

00:09:54.060 --> 00:09:55.590
The great creators.

00:09:55.590 --> 00:09:57.980
The thinkers, the artists,
the scientists, the inventors

00:09:57.980 --> 00:10:00.090
stood alone against
the men of their time.

00:10:00.090 --> 00:10:02.850
Every new thought was opposed.

00:10:02.850 --> 00:10:05.810
Every new invention
was denounced.

00:10:05.810 --> 00:10:09.150
But the men of unborrowed
vision went ahead.

00:10:09.150 --> 00:10:13.440
They fought, they suffered,
and they paid, but they won.

00:10:13.440 --> 00:10:18.600
No creator was prompted by a
desire to please his brothers.

00:10:18.600 --> 00:10:21.090
His brothers hated
the gift he offered.

00:10:21.090 --> 00:10:23.910
His truth was his only motive.

00:10:23.910 --> 00:10:26.620
His work was his only goal.

00:10:26.620 --> 00:10:29.070
RICHARD SCHMALENSEE: This
is a model of progress.

00:10:29.070 --> 00:10:30.240
Where does it come from?

00:10:30.240 --> 00:10:33.360
- --his creation, not the
benefits others derived from

00:10:33.360 --> 00:10:33.990
it.

00:10:33.990 --> 00:10:36.990
The creation which
gave form to his truth.

00:10:36.990 --> 00:10:42.330
He held his truth above all
things and against all men.

00:10:42.330 --> 00:10:45.840
He went ahead whether others
agreed with him or not,

00:10:45.840 --> 00:10:49.320
with his integrity
as his only banner.

00:10:49.320 --> 00:10:52.380
He served nothing and no one.

00:10:52.380 --> 00:10:55.380
He lived for himself.

00:10:55.380 --> 00:10:57.180
And only by living
for himself was

00:10:57.180 --> 00:11:01.320
he able to achieve the things
which are the glory of mankind.

00:11:01.320 --> 00:11:04.650
Such is the nature
of achievement.

00:11:04.650 --> 00:11:08.040
Man cannot survive
except through his mind.

00:11:08.040 --> 00:11:10.520
He comes on Earth unarmed.

00:11:10.520 --> 00:11:12.600
His brain is his only weapon.

00:11:12.600 --> 00:11:14.980
But the mind is an
attribute of the individual.

00:11:14.980 --> 00:11:18.870
There is no such thing
as a collective brain.

00:11:18.870 --> 00:11:22.800
The man who thinks must
think and act on his own.

00:11:22.800 --> 00:11:27.450
The reasoning mind cannot work
under any form of compulsion.

00:11:27.450 --> 00:11:31.410
It cannot be subordinated
to the needs, opinions,

00:11:31.410 --> 00:11:33.370
or wishes of others.

00:11:33.370 --> 00:11:36.660
It is not an object
of sacrifice.

00:11:36.660 --> 00:11:40.380
The creator stands
on his own judgment.

00:11:40.380 --> 00:11:44.640
The parasite follows
the opinions of others.

00:11:44.640 --> 00:11:46.380
The creator thinks.

00:11:46.380 --> 00:11:48.570
The parasite copies.

00:11:48.570 --> 00:11:52.110
The creator produces,
the parasite loots.

00:11:52.110 --> 00:11:55.710
The creator is concern is
the conquest of nature.

00:11:55.710 --> 00:11:58.860
The parasite's concerned
is the conquest of man.

00:11:58.860 --> 00:12:00.850
The creator requires
independence--

00:12:00.850 --> 00:12:03.120
he neither serves nor rules.

00:12:03.120 --> 00:12:07.040
He deals with men by free
exchange and voluntary choice.

00:12:07.040 --> 00:12:09.140
The parasite seeks power.

00:12:09.140 --> 00:12:10.680
He wants to bind
all men together

00:12:10.680 --> 00:12:12.983
in common action
and common slavery.

00:12:12.983 --> 00:12:13.483
He claims--

00:12:13.483 --> 00:12:15.733
RICHARD SCHMALENSEE: That's
what we call a government.

00:12:15.733 --> 00:12:17.280
- --a tool for
the use of others.

00:12:17.280 --> 00:12:20.040
That he must think as they
think, act that they act,

00:12:20.040 --> 00:12:23.120
and live in selfless,
joyless servitude

00:12:23.120 --> 00:12:25.440
to any need but his own.

00:12:25.440 --> 00:12:26.670
Look at history.

00:12:26.670 --> 00:12:29.670
Everything we have,
every great achievement

00:12:29.670 --> 00:12:34.200
has come from the independent
work of some independent mind.

00:12:34.200 --> 00:12:38.190
Every horror and destruction
came from attempts

00:12:38.190 --> 00:12:42.210
to force men into a herd of
brainless, soulless robots

00:12:42.210 --> 00:12:46.200
without personal rights,
without personal ambition,

00:12:46.200 --> 00:12:49.350
without will, hope, or dignity.

00:12:49.350 --> 00:12:51.120
It is an ancient conflict.

00:12:51.120 --> 00:12:53.210
It has another name.

00:12:53.210 --> 00:12:57.810
The individual against
the collective.

00:12:57.810 --> 00:13:00.750
Our country, the noblest
country in the history of men,

00:13:00.750 --> 00:13:03.330
was based on the principle
of individualism.

00:13:03.330 --> 00:13:07.380
The principle of man's
inalienable rights.

00:13:07.380 --> 00:13:10.500
It was a country where a man was
free to seek his own happiness,

00:13:10.500 --> 00:13:14.310
to gain and produce, not
to give up and renounce;

00:13:14.310 --> 00:13:21.330
to prosper, not to starve;
to achieve, not to plunder;

00:13:21.330 --> 00:13:25.320
to hold as his highest position
a sense of his personal value,

00:13:25.320 --> 00:13:29.760
and as his highest
virtue his self-respect.

00:13:29.760 --> 00:13:31.770
Look at the results.

00:13:31.770 --> 00:13:35.400
That is what the collectivists
are now asking you to destroy,

00:13:35.400 --> 00:13:39.300
as much of the Earth
has been destroyed.

00:13:39.300 --> 00:13:40.950
I am an architect.

00:13:40.950 --> 00:13:44.880
I know what is to come by the
principle on which it is built.

00:13:44.880 --> 00:13:48.060
We are approaching a world in
which I cannot permit myself

00:13:48.060 --> 00:13:49.530
to live.

00:13:49.530 --> 00:13:51.910
My ideas are my property.

00:13:51.910 --> 00:13:56.190
They were taken from me by
force by breach of contract.

00:13:56.190 --> 00:13:58.890
No appeal was left to me.

00:13:58.890 --> 00:14:01.320
It was believed that my
work belonged to others

00:14:01.320 --> 00:14:02.730
to do with as they pleased.

00:14:02.730 --> 00:14:05.610
That they had a claim upon
me without my consent,

00:14:05.610 --> 00:14:09.570
that it was my duty to serve
them without choice or reward.

00:14:09.570 --> 00:14:11.820
Now you know why I
dynamited Courtland.

00:14:11.820 --> 00:14:13.500
I designed Courtland.

00:14:13.500 --> 00:14:15.330
I made it possible.

00:14:15.330 --> 00:14:17.040
I destroyed it.

00:14:17.040 --> 00:14:18.960
I agreed to design
it for the purpose

00:14:18.960 --> 00:14:21.300
of seeing it built as I wished.

00:14:21.300 --> 00:14:24.150
That was the price
that I set for my work.

00:14:24.150 --> 00:14:25.860
I was not paid.

00:14:25.860 --> 00:14:27.690
My building was
disfigured at the whim

00:14:27.690 --> 00:14:29.880
of others who took all
the benefits of my work

00:14:29.880 --> 00:14:32.740
and gave me nothing in return.

