00:55:30.750 --> 00:55:31.820
Do they get rolled back?

00:55:36.290 --> 00:55:40.250
Once you've built the agency
and put the law in place,

00:55:40.250 --> 00:55:42.080
do they roll back?

00:55:42.080 --> 00:55:42.745
Jessica?

00:55:42.745 --> 00:55:43.370
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:55:43.370 --> 00:55:44.840
I'm sitting here
thinking-- because I'm

00:55:44.840 --> 00:55:45.710
