00:56:20.930 --> 00:56:22.170
to take over the markets.

00:56:22.170 --> 00:56:23.870
And that's when they turned to--

00:56:23.870 --> 00:56:26.960
let's be-- let's give
everything to this one guy.

00:56:26.960 --> 00:56:29.243
So it might also be
a preemptive attack.

00:56:29.243 --> 00:56:31.160
RICHARD SCHMALENSEE:
You're talking about Cuba

00:56:31.160 --> 00:56:35.870
before the revolution, and the
