00:56:43.130 --> 00:56:47.240
for visiting Americans, and
immense poverty for much

00:56:47.240 --> 00:56:49.150
of Cuba.

00:56:49.150 --> 00:56:52.840
And that government
lost legitimacy.

00:56:52.840 --> 00:56:58.860
And you got central action,
which brought a lot of literacy

00:56:58.860 --> 00:57:02.190
to the Cuban people,
improved medical care,

00:57:02.190 --> 00:57:04.770
and, well, better than it was.

00:57:04.770 --> 00:57:10.890
And of course, now we're back
to grinding poverty again now

00:57:10.890 --> 00:57:12.850
that the Soviet support
is gone, but yeah.

00:57:12.850 --> 00:57:14.850
AUDIENCE: But the system
of checks and balances,

00:57:14.850 --> 00:57:17.310
having that flexibility
to like open--

00:57:17.310 --> 00:57:20.400
to give government more power
