everything will solve itself
without these tyrannical laws

01:05:16.710 --> 01:05:19.450
that are just inappropriate
in this situation.

01:05:19.450 --> 01:05:22.000
RICHARD SCHMALENSEE: Minimum
wage law is a tyrannical law.

