Okey-doke.

01:05:23.140 --> 01:05:23.748
I'm with you.

01:05:23.748 --> 01:05:24.290
I'm with you.

01:05:24.290 --> 01:05:24.950
I got it.

01:05:24.950 --> 01:05:25.450
No, no.

01:05:25.450 --> 01:05:26.440
You just play the role.

01:05:26.440 --> 01:05:27.750
Yeah.

01:05:27.750 --> 01:05:29.250
AUDIENCE: I'm kind
of a right-winger

01:05:29.250 --> 01:05:31.750
in enemy territory over here.

01:05:31.750 --> 01:05:33.850
But I'd say, like,
